  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Loan Operations Analyst",
  "description": "<p>Our client is an international bank and they have a few job openings for the Loan Operations Analyst position<br /></p><p></p><p><strong>This is a  1 year contract position</strong><br /></p><p></p><p>The Loans Operations Analyst role is a key support function responsible for the <strong>accurate, timely, and compliant end-to-end processing and servicing</strong> of loan products (syndicated, bilateral, revolving) and Banker's Guarantees (BGs) for the bank's Asia Pacific lending businesses.</p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Loan & BG Servicing</strong></p><ul><li>Executes all transaction lifecycle events (drawdowns, rate fixing, rollovers, repayments, BG issuance/amendments).</li></ul><p><strong>System & Data</strong></p><ul><li>Inputs and verifies critical loan/BG data in core banking systems (e.g., Avaloq, Kondor) and manages Nostro funding/reconciliation.</li></ul><p><strong>Risk & Compliance</strong></p><ul><li>Performs checks against AML policies, adheres to operational risk guidelines, and ensures control procedures are followed.</li></ul><p><strong>Reporting</strong></p><ul><li>Conducts daily position reconciliation and prepares mandatory periodic reports for internal stakeholders (Finance, Compliance), Head Office, regulatory bodies (MAS, HKMA), and external clients/auditors.</li></ul><p><strong>Efficiency</strong></p><ul><li>Supports process improvement initiatives to enhance system workflows and reduce manual processing.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><ul><li><p><strong>Experience:</strong> 3 to 5 years in <strong>Loan Operations</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Education:</strong> Bachelor's/Master's in Finance, Business, or Engineering.</p></li><li><p><strong>Skills:</strong> Independent worker, strong team player, multi-tasking under pressure, and Microsoft Office proficiency.<br /></p></li></ul><p>This is an <strong>operations and control role</strong> critical for ensuring the smooth execution, accurate record-keeping, and regulatory compliance of all lending transactions<br /></p><p></p><p><br />Applicants who are keen to apply for this position can send your latest resume to alfred.lai@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Alfred Lai</p><p>EA Reg No: R1545971</p><p>EA License No: 21C0434</p>",
